==English==

===Etymology===
A saints' name from the {{etyl|la|en}} gens name {{m|la|Ignatius}}, {{m|la|Egnatius}}, of uncertain meaning, by [[folk etymology]] associated with Latin {{m|la|ignis||fire}}. It might be related to Ancient Greek {{l|grc|ἴγνης||indigene}}, {{m|grc|ἴγνητος}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|lang=en|/ɪɡˈneɪʃəs/}}
* {{hyph|Ig|na|tius|lang=en}}

===Proper noun===
